82
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,740
even if we get married...

83
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,360
♪Wishing for a bit more♪

84
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:44,740
I will no longer love you

85
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,340
or see you again.

86
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:50,500
♪You and I, each completing the other,
year after year♪

87
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:52,300
That would be for the best.

